@8482 = ~The oldest scraps of tale hint at this armor's original bearer: a nigh-mythical slayer of demons who was said to rip and tear their flesh with his bare hands, carving a wrathful path through infernal hosts. Whether the Doomplate remembers that champion, hungers for such purpose again, or merely amplifies the will of any who stride into the jaws of the abyss… none can say.

Now empowered with the hearts of demons, this armor is now an incredibly powerful tool against the hordes of both the Abyss and the Hells.

