@50000 = ~Ring of Elemental Mastery
This ring combines the might of elements of Earth, Air and Fire and grants the user dominion over the creatures that hail from those planes. This ring was created for <CHARNAME> and its fame will no doubt grow with <PRO_HIMHER>.

STATISTICS:

Equipped abilities:
– Armor Class: +1
– Saving Throws: +1
– Fire, Electricity, and Acid Resistance: +50%

Charge abilities:
– Summon 24-HD Greater Air, Earth, and Fire Elemental once per day
  Range: 20 ft.
  Duration: 1 hour

– Charm Air, Earth, or Fire Elemental three times per day (no save)
  Range: Touch
  Duration: 60 seconds
  Area of Effect: 1 elemental

– Improved Invisibility once per day
  Range: Touch
  Duration: 1 turn
  Area of Effect: 1 creature

Weight: 0~

@50010 = ~Boots of the Hornet
The Boots of the Hornet are unsurpassed at increased the speed of their wearer. Combining all of the powers of the Boots of Avoidance and the Boots of Speed, these boots make it very difficult to strike the bearer indeed.

STATISTICS:

